result.description:
This is a follow-up to a request, I fulfil most, so go ahead and describe the pic you want in the comments or send an imgur link to it. If you find a better-quality image put an imgur link to it in the comments.

Credits go to Xperiaz1, who was the creator and for unknown reasons deleted the art, a link to the image is found in the code, and >Beca< for the colour choices.

This code was created by me, do give feedback for improvements in the comments.
If you want more fixed roblox styles just click BoopBop at the top, or you can click DittoDino below for some mediocre youtube progressbars.
